==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
Literally: one action, two gains

===Idiom===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' yī jǔ liǎng dé)
# [[kill two birds with one stone]]; do one task and finish two or more goals

===Synonyms===
* [[一箭双雕]]
* [[一石二鸟]]

